EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
BAY OF BISCAY.
1. TEN METER S/V JONATHAN LS, BLUE HULL, CAPSIZED AND
   ADRIFT IN 47-13N 005-31W ON 29 SEP. ONE OR MORE PERSONS
   BELIEVED TO BE IN A LIFERAFT VICINITY 47-15N 004-15W.
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
   ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC ETEL, TELEX: 42950519,
   PHONE: 332 9755 3535, FAX: 332 9755 4934,
   E-MAIL: ETEL@MRCCFR.EU.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2279/12.
